<dl id="n40122c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40122c">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40122c"> 122(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> houri </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: A <i>houri</i> is an extremely beautiful young woman. In Islam, a houri exists in Paradise as a divine companion for those believers who have died. The Persian root, <i>huri</i>, means &ldquo;nymph in Paradise,&rdquo; from the Arabic <i>haura</i>, &ldquo;beautifully dark-eyed.&rdquo; </mm> </dd></dl>
